{"topic": "OpenZWave/1/node/6/", "msg": "{\n    \"NodeID\": 6,\n    \"NodeQueryStage\": \"Complete\",\n    \"isListening\": true,\n    \"isFlirs\": false,\n    \"isBeaming\": true,\n    \"isRouting\": true,\n    \"isSecurityv1\": false,\n    \"isZWavePlus\": true,\n    \"isNIFRecieved\": true,\n    \"isAwake\": true,\n    \"isFailed\": false,\n    \"MetaData\": {\n        \"OZWInfoURL\": \"http://www.openzwave.com/device-database/027a:a002:a000\",\n        \"ZWAProductURL\": \"\",\n        \"ProductPic\": \"images/zooz/zen27.png\",\n        \"Description\": \"Product features: - Manual or Z-Wave on/off and brightness control - Simple Direct 3-Way: connect with existing on/off switches in 3-way, 4-way, and 5-way set-ups, no add-on needed (neutral wire required) - Fully adjustable ramp rate for just the right on/off speed - Double tap to full brightness feature - Remembers and restores on/off status after power failure - LED indicator signals inclusion, exclusion, reset, and setting changes - Built-in Z-Wave Plus signal repeater to extend network range - Extended compatibility with LED bulbs, no more flickering! - S2 security protocol and the latest 500 Z-Wave chip for faster and safer wireless communication - Customizable LED indicator and air-gap switch for added safety SPECIFICATIONS: - Model Number: ZEN27 - Z-Wave Signal Frequency: 908.42 MHz - Power: 120 VAC, 60 Hz - Maximum Load: 100 W LED/CFL, 300 W incandescent (100 W with both sides of heat sink tabs off) - Range: Up to 100 feet line of sight - Operating Temperature: 32-104\u00b0 F (0-40\u00b0 C) - Installation and Use: Indoor only https://www.support.getzooz.com/kb/article/314-zooz-s2-dimmer-zen27-ver-2-08-advanced-settings/ MANUAL CONTROL Upper Paddle: 1 x tap: load on to last / custom brightness; Scene 1, attribute 00 (button 1) 2 x tap: on to full / max brightness; Scene 1, attribute 03 (button 3) 3 x tap: enter inclusion (pairing) mode; Scene 1, attribute 04 (button 5) 4 x tap: Scene 1, attribute 05 (button 7) 6 x tap: change LED indicator mode (see parameter 2) 10 x tap: change physical / Z-Wave control mode (see parameter 15) press and hold: increase brightness level tap-tap-tap-and-hold: factory reset Lower Paddle: 1 x tap: load off; Scene 2, attribute 00 (button 2) 2 x tap: Scene 2, attribute 03 (button 4) 3 x tap: enter exclusion (unpairing) mode; Scene 2, attribute 04 (button 6) 4 x tap: Scene 2, attribute 05 (button 8) press and hold: decrease brightness level tap-tap-tap-and-hold: factory reset\",\n        \"ProductManualURL\": \"https://products.z-wavealliance.org/ProductManual/File?folder=&filename=MarketCertificationFiles/3148/zooz-z-wave-plus-s2-dimmer-switch-zen27-manual.pdf\",\n        \"ProductPageURL\": \"\",\n        \"InclusionHelp\": \"1. Initiate inclusion (pairing) in the app (or web interface) of your hub. 2. Tap the upper paddle on the switch 3 times quickly.\",\n        \"ExclusionHelp\": \"1. Bring your Z-Wave gateway (hub) close to the switch if possible 2. Put the Z-Wave hub into exclusion mode (not sure how to do that? ask@getzooz.com) 3. Tap the lower paddle on the switch 3 times quickly\",\n        \"ResetHelp\": \"If your primary controller is missing or inoperable, you may need to reset the device to factory settings. To complete the reset process manually, tap-tap-tap\u2019n\u2019hold the upper paddle for at least 10 seconds. The LED indicator will flash to confirm successful reset. NOTE: All previously recorded activity and custom settings will be erased from the device\u2019s memory.\",\n        \"WakeupHelp\": \"\",\n        \"ProductSupportURL\": \"\",\n        \"Frequency\": \"\",\n        \"Name\": \"S2 Dimmer\",\n        \"ProductPicBase64\": \"\"\n    },\n    \"Event\": \"nodeQueriesComplete\",\n    \"TimeStamp\": 1624317729,\n    \"NodeManufacturerName\": \"Zooz\",\n    \"NodeProductName\": \"ZEN27 S2 Dimmer Wall Switch\",\n    \"NodeBasicString\": \"Routing Slave\",\n    \"NodeBasic\": 4,\n    \"NodeGenericString\": \"Multilevel Switch\",\n    \"NodeGeneric\": 17,\n    \"NodeSpecificString\": \"Multilevel Power Switch\",\n    \"NodeSpecific\": 1,\n    \"NodeManufacturerID\": \"0x027a\",\n    \"NodeProductType\": \"0xa000\",\n    \"NodeProductID\": \"0xa002\",\n    \"NodeBaudRate\": 100000,\n    \"NodeVersion\": 4,\n    \"NodeGroups\": 2,\n    \"NodeName\": \"\",\n    \"NodeLocation\": \"\",\n    \"NodeDeviceTypeString\": \"Light Dimmer Switch Wall Lamp\",\n    \"NodeDeviceType\": 1540,\n    \"NodeRole\": 5,\n    \"NodeRoleString\": \"Always On Slave\",\n    \"NodePlusType\": 0,\n    \"NodePlusTypeString\": \"Z-Wave+ node\",\n    \"Neighbors\": [\n        7\n    ],\n    \"Neighbors\": [\n        7\n    ]\n}"}
